entries.femaleVariant: You think it will take the load?
Who cares? The parade is starting soon.
Yeah, that does look pretty great...
Saburo Arasaka, the poor chap. World's most powerful turned into a commercial hack.
Surprised? He's a symbol, an icon.
Even in death, his net worth's increased markedly…
Hey, what's going on? Why'd you shut the elevators down?
Security reasons.
Are you fucking kidding me? You want me to take the stairs all the way down?
There are quicker ways, if you are interested? No? The stairs, then.
Come on, waste of words.
It'll be beautiful! Just the juxtaposition of the masses celebratin' corporate culture and havin' exactly no share in its capital.
Uhh... How's this?
Preem! Hot! Oh! I'm 'onna spew a load!
Hell'd you just do?
Don't wanna know, believe me.
Don't wanna know, man, trust me. For your own good.
Yeah, sure, I get it. Forget I asked!
Awww, ya'll can go fuck yourselves…!
They killed Tom and didn't even bother releasin' his body! And there ain't no compensation 'thout no body!
Cool it, all right?! Ya can't know who's listenin'!
No surprises here. All the factions have peeps on the ground.
No, don't think so. It is Arasaka, y'know. If there was going to be any blood-letting, they'd do it behind closed doors.
Whoa, ain't that somethin'!
I have this scrolled! You can't treat people this way!
And the corp will show it all off in Night City…
Lemme see it, now... Lemme see that fuckin' juxtaposition…
Hush up! You crazy?!
Tha'ss the motherfuckin' problem! Nobody's listenin'!
I suppose we're not nearly as independent here as we make ourselves out to be…
Hyenas! Murderers and fuckin' thieves, tha'ss what they are!
V! Find cover! They see you!
You should be safe there.
Phew, that was close.
Be careful now...
V, do you wish to die?! Get back behind cover!
V, this is important. Oda is speaking to someone.
Again. Security is substandard! It meets none of our norms!
Hanako-sama should not be here!
You questioning Yorinobu's orders?
Do your damn job.
Understood. Over and out.
Mhh, it is just as we expected. Oda is here.
Holmes, shouldn't even be out here. Back inside, back inside.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="ese" b="Aww, c'mon, " a=". It's beautiful! Not often ya get a whole bag full of eye candy."/>
Access point's hella secure anyways. Placed mines around it, get me? Anyone breathes on it – poof! They'll be turned into a cloud of confetti.
Yeah. I got work here, man. So not coming down. You manage on your own.
Yes, that is the access hatch of the system. Ask the techie men. Maybe dey help you.
I will contact you with any news.
I am linking you in. We both can listen.
I know that borged out ogre!
Adam fuckin' Smasher!
Guy who killed you?
Chill. Sure it was him?
Guy who killed you, right?
Guy?! Motherfucker's barely human!
Chill out a sec. Sure it was him?
I'd recognize that voice anywhere!
But hey – know what? I'm glad he's here.
Catwalk don't look too stable…
Sure Takemura didn't plan a little "whoopsy-daisy" for ya?
Told ya so.
Sniper! He can see you! Hide!
Stay hidden!
Not yet, V!
You must be more careful.
Wait there until it is calm. I will signal you.
Remember, they can still detect you.
You're glad?
Seein' as I woke up in a world without any Saburo, I'll have to be satisfied with Smasher.
You gotta be satisfied? You got fuck-all to lose!
All right, fine – we. Your finger on the fuckin' trigger, I guess.
